I"x<p>The supported platforms are <code>state</code>, <code>numeric_state</code>, and <code>template</code>. They are modeled after their corresponding triggers for automations, requiring <code>to_state</code> (for <code>state</code>), <code>below</code> and/or <code>above</code> (for <code>numeric_state</code>) and <code>value_template</code> (for <code>template</code>).</p>
